children.topic:
****See below information on how to get started and how to play/catch pokemon.****


*Random Pokemon will spawn in this channel and you will then have a chance to catch them! Normal conversation in any of the channels go towards spawning pokemon.
Spamming by a single person does not make Pokemon appear.*

Tag Pokemon Bot and type **start** to get started and have the chance to catch pokemon

Tag Pokemon Bot and type **pick (starter name)**- to select a starter (gen 1 thru 7)

Now you ready to go! Whenever a pokemon appears type -

Tag Pokemon and type **catch (pokemon name)**- the first to correctly enter this gets the pokemon

Tag Pokemon Bot and type **hint** will offer a hint at the name.
